  <brief_title>Trial Comparing Routine Intraoperative Transesophageal Echocardiography During Radical Cystectomy to Standard of Care</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Control Trial Comparing Routine Intraoperative Transesophageal Echocardiography During Radical Cystectomy to Standard of Care</official_title>
